quran[82]{c,v,t}:
  100,9,Na ha a tsebe hore mohla mabitla a hlatsang likateng
  100,10,Se ka lifubeng tsa batho se tla behoa pepeneneng
  100,11,Letsatsing leo Mong`a bona U tlabe A tseba tsohle tsa bona
  101,1,Sekhobo
  101,2,Sekhobo ke eng
  101,3,Ebe ke eng se tla le tsebisa hore na sekhobo ke eng
  101,4,Ke letsatsi leo batho ba tla hasana joaloka lirurubele
  101,5,Lithaba li tla ba joalo ka boea
  101,6,Bao liketso tsa bona li tla imela sekala
  101,7,Ba tla phela bophelo ba nyakallo
  101,8,Empa eo liketso tsa hae li tla fokola sekaleng
  101,9,Lehae la hae e tla ba Lihele
  101,10,E be ke eng se tla le tsebisa hore na lihele ke eng
  101,11,Ke mollo o hlenneng
  102,1,Phehisano ea pokello ea matlotlo e le khelositse
  102,2,Ho fihlela le etela mabitleng
  102,3,Che! Haufinyane le tla tseba
  102,4,Hape le tla tseba
  102,5,Che! Hoja le na le tsebo e tehileng
  102,6,Hobane le tla bona mollo oa Lihele
  102,7,Hape le tla o bona ka tiieo
  102,8,Letsatsing leo le tla botsoa khahlano le monyaka oa lefats’e lena
  103,1,Ka Nako
  103,2,Ruri! Motho o tahlehong
  103,3,"Kantle ho ba-kholoang, ba etsang liketso tse lokileng, ba khothalletsang ‘nete le ba nang le mamello"
  104,1,Sekhobo se be ho moqabanyi e mong le e mong le raleshano
  104,2,Ea khobokantseng leruo la lefats’e lena le ho le bala
  104,3,O nahana hore leruo la hae le tla etsa hore a phele kahosafeleng
  104,4,Che! Ruri! O tla tjebeloa mollong o harinyang
  104,5,E be ke eng se tla le tsebisa hore mollo o harinyang
  104,6,Ke mollo oa Allah U hotelitsoeng
  104,7,Oo qhomelang holim’a lipelo tsa batho
  104,8,Ruri! o tlaba kupetsa
  104,9,Kahar’a lits’iea tse otlolotsoeng
  105,1,Na ha u ea bona kamoo Mong`a hau A ileng A ripitla balekane ba tlou kateng
  105,2,Ha A ka A nyopisa morero oa bona
  105,3,A romella mohlape oa linonyana khahlano le bona
  105,4,Ho ba furuletsa ka majoe a lenyetana
  105,5,A ba fetola lehlare
  106,1,Ka selekane sa Ma-Qureysh
  106,2,Re ile Ra etsa hore ba simolle maeto mariha le lehlabula
  106,3,Ha ba khumamele Mong`a ntlo ena
  106,4,Ea ba fepang khahlanong le tlala le ho ba sireletsa matsoalong a bona
  107,1,U kile oa bona motho ea latolang kahlolo
  107,2,Ke ea lelekang khutsana
  107,3,Ea sa khothaletseng ho feptjoa ha mafutsana
  107,4,Aa! Sekhobo se be holim’a barapeli
  107,5,Ba sa tsotelleng thapelo ea bona
  107,6,Ba etsetsang ho bonoa
  107,7,Ba hana ka litokelo tsa boahisane
  108,1,Ruri Re u nehile tlotla ea Seliba Paradeising
  108,2,"Kahoo, retelehela ho Mong`a hau ka thapelo, u etse sehlabelo"
  108,3,Ruri! Ke sera sa hau se tlang ho hloka bokamoso
  109,1,"E re: “Oho lona mahana-tumelo"
  109,2,Ha ke khumamele seo le se khumamelang
  109,3,Le lona ha le khumamele seo ke se khumamelang
  109,4,Ha nkeke ka khumamela seo le se khumamelang
  109,5,Etsoe le ke keng la khumamela seo ke se khumamelang
  109,6,"Tumelo ea lona ke ea lona, ea ka ke ea ka"
  110,1,Ha thuso le tlholo ea Allah li fihlang
  110,2,U bona lichaba li inehela tumelong ea Allah ka mekhopi
  110,3,"Keteka lithoriso tsa Mong`a hau, kopa ts’oarelo ho Eena: ke Eena Ea amohelang boinyatso, Ea Ts`oarelang"
  111,1,Ha mats`oho a Lahab a timele! Ha a timele
  111,2,Ha ho moputso maruong a hae le ho tseo a li bokellelitseng
  111,3,Haufi o tlaba mollong o khanare ea lelakabe
  111,4,Mohatsa`e o tla roala patsi e le libeso
  111,5,Thapo e lohiloeng ka makhapetla a palema e haretsoe molaleng oa hae (mohatsae)
  112,1,"E re: Ke Allah, Ea Inotsi"
  112,2,"Allah, Rabosafeleng"
  112,3,"Ha A tsoale, ha A tsoaloa"
  112,4,Ha ho ea ts’oanang le Eena
  113,1,"E re: Ke kopa ts’ireletso ho Mong`a meso"
  113,2,Khahlanong le tse silafetseng tse hlotsoeng
  113,3,Ka ho ts’oana le tse silafetseng tsa lefifing le noelletseng
  113,4,Le khahlanong le bobe ba balohi ba mafito
  113,5,Le khahlanong le bobe ba bahonuhi ha ba honoha
  114,1,"E re: ke kopa ts’ireletso ho Mong`a batho bohle"
  114,2,Morena oa batho
  114,3,Mopi oa batho
  114,4,"Khahlanong le linyonts`a tsa mosebi ea soto, ea hoeshetsang a be a nyamele"
  114,5,Ea silafatsang lipelo tsa batho
  114,6,Har’a masabonoeng (li-jinn) le har`a batho